From: Marshall Booth <mbooth+@pitt.edu>
Organization: University of Pittsburgh School of Medicine
To: "Mailshell User" <nospam@mailshell.com>
Subject: Re: [Mercedes] OE W114 tires?

The original 175x14 or 6.95x14 tires are probably most close to an 80
aspect ratio tire (someone once told me they actually had an 83 aspect
ratio, but I've never confirmed that). A 185/75x14 will be very close as
will the original 175S14. Yokohama makes a 185/75x14 Avid Touring tire
with an 80kmi warranty and a $40 price tag.

Marshall
